{"type": "article", "id": 22694, "title": "酒吧环境的吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-23T07:30:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153248CrP4JHT2cDRXahvU.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是两家设计品牌 Cerno 和 ICRAVE 联合推出的灯，一共有两种，都采用三角木架和金属灯罩的组合，不同只在于灯罩的长短和与支架的位置，一个用三角支架支撑，另一个像是滑到了下面。两盏灯都带有一点工业味道，适合暗色调的地方。灯罩有多种颜色，售价 1494 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.ylighting.com/cerno-imber-pendant-light.html\">这里是购买链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153245M3GdHOLkUW2FgiKR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153245WScITCNYvHoJm7L9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153246S3W0eGOhi7fo8N4R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153247m3CvhKjtQyknVXqY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}